snippet.title: Alohomora - The True Emperor (Lyrical) | The Devil | Darshan | Prakash Veer | B Ajaneesh Loknath
snippet.description:
For more latest songs & videos, subscribe ðŸ‘‰ https://bit.ly/Saregama_Kannada

Presenting the Lyrical of ''Alohomora - The True Emperor'' from the movie ''The Devil'' starring Challenging Star Darshan, Rachana Rai and others. Shri Jaimatha Combines, in association with Saregama a Yoodlee Films, presents the much-awaited film The Devil.

Name: Alohomora - The True Emperor
Music Composed, Arranged & Programmed By: B Ajaneesh Loknath
Singer: Aniruddha Sastry
Lyrics: Aniruddha Sastry
Choreographer: Santhu Master
Keyboard: B Ajaneesh Loknath, Raja Ravi Varma

       (With immense sorrow in our hearts, we bring to you Heart-throb Yatra, in association with Studio Chant Audio Vision and NK Production.
This is our humble tribute to Zubeen Garg, the voice we grew up with, the music that healed us, the artist who became our own.
More than 100 artistes and the entire musical/technical fraternity of Assam have joined hands in this special journey to honour his unforgettable contribution to our music, our culture, and our lives.)
Heart-throb Yatra is our way of saying thank you...for the songs that made us smile, for the lyrics that gave us strength and for being the heartbeat of Assam.

       (With immense sorrow in our hearts, we bring to you Heart-throb Yatra, in association with Studio Chant Audio Vision and NK Production.
This is our humble tribute to Zubeen Garg, the voice we grew up with, the music that healed us, the artist who became our own.
More than 100 artistes and the entire musical/technical fraternity of Assam have joined hands in this special journey to honour his unforgettable contribution to our music, our culture, and our lives.)
Heart-throb Yatra is our way of saying thank you...for the songs that made us smile, for the lyrics that gave us strength and for being the heartbeat of Assam.

snippet.title: Friends (4K) | Official Trailer | Vijay | Suriya | Vadivelu | Siddique
snippet.description:
A man values his best friend more than anything else in the world. One day he confesses a dark secret from their childhood to his wife, which is overheard by another. Once the secret gets out, the friendship is destroyed.

Movie Credits:

Directed by: Siddique
Written by: Siddique

Mahesh Babu, collaborating with Rajamouli for the first time. His introduction at the event â€” riding a mechanical white bull â€” mirrored his ferocious on-screen first look as a blood-streaked warrior wielding a trident.

Priyanka Chopra, returning to Indian cinema after several Hollywood projects, plays Mandakini. Prithviraj Sukumaran, introduced earlier this month as the antagonist Kumbha, described his role as â€œphysically and emotionally exhausting,â€

Telugu | Mahesh Babu | Priyanka Chopra | SS Rajamouli | Cinemondo! #varanasi #varanastrailer ##varanasitrailerreaction #ssrajamouli #trailerreaction Kathy and Mark react to Varanasi To the World! Varanasi (stylised as VÄranÄsi) is an upcoming Indian Telugu-language action-adventure film directed by S. S. Rajamouli, who co-wrote the screenplay with V. Vijayendra Prasad. T the film stars Mahesh Babu, Priyanka Chopra and Prithviraj Sukumaran. Rajamouli conceived the film as a globetrotting action adventure rooted in Indian cultural themes, drawing inspiration from the structure and emotional tone of classic adventure cinema.

Varanasi (ditulis sebagai VÄranÄsi) adalah film aksi-petualangan berbahasa Telugu India yang akan datang yang disutradarai oleh S. S. Rajamouli, yang ikut menulis skenarionya dengan V. Vijayendra Prasad. Film ini dibintangi oleh Mahesh Babu, Priyanka Chopra, dan Prithviraj Sukumaran. Rajamouli menggagas film ini sebagai petualangan aksi keliling dunia yang berakar pada tema-tema budaya India, mengambil inspirasi dari struktur dan nada emosional sinema petualangan klasik.

en-US.title: VARANASI to the WORLD Reaction! Telugu | Mahesh Babu | Priyanka Chopra | SS Rajamouli | Cinemondo!
en-US.description:
VARANASI to the WORLD Reaction! Telugu | Mahesh Babu | Priyanka Chopra | SS Rajamouli | Cinemondo! #varanasi #varanastrailer ##varanasitrailerreaction #ssrajamouli #trailerreaction Kathy and Mark react to Varanasi To the World! Varanasi (stylised as VÄranÄsi) is an upcoming Indian Telugu-language action-adventure film directed by S. S. Rajamouli, who co-wrote the screenplay with V. Vijayendra Prasad. T the film stars Mahesh Babu, Priyanka Chopra and Prithviraj Sukumaran. Rajamouli conceived the film as a globetrotting action adventure rooted in Indian cultural themes, drawing inspiration from the structure and emotional tone of classic adventure cinema.

it.title: VARANASI alla reazione del MONDO! Telugu | Mahesh Babu | Priyanka Chopra | SS Rajamouli | Cinemando!
it.description:
Reazione a VARANASI to the WORLD! Telugu | Mahesh Babu | Priyanka Chopra | SS Rajamouli | Cinemondo! #varanasi #varanastrailer ##varanasitrailerreaction #ssrajamouli #trailerreaction Kathy e Mark reagiscono a Varanasi To the World! Varanasi (stilizzato come VÄranÄsi) Ã¨ un film d'azione e avventura indiano in lingua telugu di prossima uscita, diretto da S. S. Rajamouli, che ha co-scritto la sceneggiatura con V. Vijayendra Prasad. Il film vede protagonisti Mahesh Babu, Priyanka Chopra e Prithviraj Sukumaran. Rajamouli ha concepito il film come un'avventura d'azione in giro per il mondo, radicata nei temi culturali indiani, traendo ispirazione dalla struttura e dal tono emotivo del cinema d'avventura classico.

snippet.title: ekÅ - Malayalam Movie|Official Trailer| Sandeep Pradeep|Dinjith Ayyathan| Mujeeb Majeed|Bahul Ramesh
snippet.description:
Presenting the official trailer of ekÅ, directed by Dinjith Ayyathan, following his acclaimed film Kishkindha Kaandam. Written by Bahul Ramesh, ekÅ marks the final chapter of his Animal Trilogy after Kishkindha Kaandam and Kerala Crime Files: Season 2, forming a collection of three standalone stories sharing a spiritual essence â€” exploring crimes and moral conflicts in a world where animal presence plays a stimulating role. 

The film also marks the maiden production venture of Mr. MRK Jhayaram under his banner Aaradyaa Studios.

Stream and Listen to the teaser track 'Eko Intro Theme' on your favourite audio streaming platforms - http://tinysync.in/oG_f1C_xnAE

Directed by : Dinjith Ayyathan 
Produced by: MRK Jhayaram
Story, Screenplay, Dialogues & DOP : Bahul Ramesh  
Music : Mujeeb Majeed 
Editor : Sooraj E S
Art Director : Sajeesh Thamarassery
Production Controller : Shafi Chemmad
Audiography : Vishnu Govind 
Make Up: Rasheed Ahammed 
Costume Design: Sujith Sudhakaran 
Project Designer : Sandeep Sasidharan
DI : Color Planet Studios
Colourist : Srik Varier
Trailer Cut : Mahesh Bhuvanend
Chief Associate Director : Sagar
VFX : IVFX
Stills: Rinson M B 
Marketing & Designs : Yellowtooths
Subtitles : Vivek Renjit (Break Borders) 
PRO : Pratheesh Sekhar
Digital Marketing : Akhil Vishnu VS
Visual Promotions : Snakeplant LLP
Cast : Sandeep Pradeep, Vineeth, Narain, Binu Pappu, Ashokan, Biana Momin, Sim Zhi Fei, NG Hung Shen, Ranjith Shekhar, Saheer Muhammed
Label : Muzik247
